            "rows": "Did you get the Audit Plan sufficiently in advance? | \r\nWas the audit team well prepared for audit? | \r\nWas the audit carried out as per the programme? | \r\nWas the opening and closing meeting carried out professionally? | \r\nDid the audit team give you enough explanation for your questions? | \r\nAudit team didn’t make any unreasonable demand? | \r\nWould you like the same auditor to audit your organization in future? | \r\nDid your queries were responded promptly? | \r\nDid you get the audit report and certificates in reasonable time? | \r\nDid issues found at the audit were helpful and valuable for improving your management system?",
